？香港唔係中國嗎？想分裂中國嗎？"},{"pid":"0493a5c00305ecaa1623a254ab3b546e3ddacadd","tid":2140561,"uid":323254,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T08:27:28.000Z","msg":"屌，今日甩P呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，可以推呀"},{"pid":"35e50bccf80c062f65f930200523052759c2811b","tid":2140561,"uid":147024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T08:29:25.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ad1e9945751d4eef0dd98c63057cac87262868db","tid":2140561,"uid":263577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T08:29:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cfdfc5702f48da4fa4a1768802ed905efa28b361","tid":2140561,"uid":147024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T08:31:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8d0adc39f897336bf5904336c739e360e438fe1","tid":2140561,"uid":263577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4dab055037e7428f2cb607050da2fc8d054f69c1","tid":2140561,"uid":263577,"like":76,"dislike":5,"score":71,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T06:04:08.000Z","msg":"樓主好波，行內人都質疑理大藥研既能力，你呢個post更加印證呢點，<br />\n<br />\n佢呢隻睇落去係virus inhibitor, 並唔能夠刺激產生免疫力，我咁講岩唔岩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T08:34:02.000Z","msg":"我錯撚左concept 勿like, 費事有人當左係岩"},{"pid":"fd486bfb39064f9442db4678054d81b7cee4ad3c","tid":2140561,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5d7114884f513f156c490e19a19be7740f1a7de","tid":2140561,"uid":268153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T05:37:41.000Z","msg":"【理大疫苗？港澳疫苗？四川疫苗至真！】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/68kQdtK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F68kQdtK.jpg&h=ba94a712&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n理工大學同澳門科技大學日前公佈成功「共同研發」武漢肺炎疫苗，並有望於短期內進行臨床測試。香港各大媒體，甚至外媒都瘋狂吹捧呢劑「理大疫苗」、「港澳疫苗」，視為對抗武漢肺炎嘅希望。<br />\n<br />\n呢種疫苗實質係一隻重組RBD蛋白（recombinant Receptor Binding Domain protein），能夠同武漢肺炎病毒進入人體細胞嘅主要通道 &mdash; ACE2結合，令武肺病毒無法進入細胞，從而產生預防作用。不過，呢個唔係科普Post，今日想講嘅係，呢隻疫苗根本唔係「港澳研發」或者「理大研發」。<br />\n<br />\n理大應用生物及化學科技學系客座教授劉耀南指出，今次疫苗備受重視，著名科學期刊《自然》（&rdquo;Nature&ldquo;）亦提早刊登佢哋嘅學術文章。好學嘅我就當然即刻上Nature觀摩下香港院校嘅研究成果。一㩒入去，神奇嘅事情就發生了，文章由88位學者共同撰寫，當中有48位來自四川大學生物治療國家重點實驗室；23位來自中國衛健委直接管理嘅中國醫學科學院，來自香港嘅就只有劉耀南（Johnson Yiu-Nam Lau）一人，來自澳門嘅亦都只有澳門科技大學醫學院教授張康（Kang Zhang）等二人。作者資訊一欄更指出，文章嘅主要作者為7位分別出身自四川大學同中國醫學科學院嘅學者。今次嘅研究徹頭徹尾都難以稱得上係一個「港澳研究」，甚至係「理大研究」項目。<br />\n<br />\n好大喜功係中國嘅習性，成功研發武漢肺炎疫苗，正常必定會公告天下，並向各國「伸出援手」，但點解今次會如此強調疫苗係「港澳研究」呢？實在耐人尋味。到底係有人希望利用香港學術界嘅聲譽同埋貿易網絡令疫苗更容易得到外國信任，定係另有打算？我相信大家自有判斷。<br />\n<br />\n相關學術文章：<a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/s41586-020-2599-8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41586-020-2599-8&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7Zeamo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=e330fd6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/s41586-020-2599-8</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n梁晃維 Fergus Leung<br />\n中西區區議員（觀龍) <br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n休戚與共 長風破浪<br />\n📷Instagram | <a href=\"http://instagram.com/fergus.lfw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Ffergus.lfw&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7Zeamo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=fe877ab7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">instagram.com/fergus.lfw</a><br />\n🐤Twitter | <a href=\"http://twitter.com/FergusLeung\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FFergusLeung&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7Zeamo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=4adad9da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">twitter.com/FergusLeung</a><br />\n<br />\n#梁晃維 #FergusLeung<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100589934628086/posts/307485257271885/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100589934628086%2Fposts%2F307485257271885%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7Zeamo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=14b17d63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100589934628086/posts/307485257271885/?d=n</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T08:37:40.000Z","msg":"呢種疫苗係舊技術，係用來製造呼感道病毒疫苗"},{"pid":"27e1b4a89702bdeab5876e013914106325f971e1","tid":2140561,"uid":38861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4dab055037e7428f2cb607050da2fc8d054f69c1","tid":2140561,"uid":263577,"like":76,"dislike":5,"score":71,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T06:04:08.000Z","msg":"樓主好波，行內人都質疑理大藥研既能力，你呢個post更加印證呢點，<br />\n<br />\n佢呢隻睇落去係virus inhibitor, 並唔能夠刺激產生免疫力，我咁講岩唔岩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T08:37:45.000Z","msg":"佢呢隻睇落去係virus inhibitor, 並唔能夠刺激產生免疫力，我咁講岩唔岩。<br />\n<br />\n唔啱，唔計幾隻用弱化武肺病毒做疫苗的話，事實上主流係針對武肺病毒的RBD或者S protein嚟製造疫苗，美國Moderna、牛津及中國某間進行緊Phase3的疫苗都係target S protein位置（運輸的手法各自不同，Moderna用mRNA、牛津同某間中國用不同的adenovirus vector)，從而促使人體產生相應的抗體。"},{"pid":"915673a89a5451c500b1e6db6ec3137ebb12411b","tid":2140561,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T08:40:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6592c1fa3dafa8d61c1e4fa6adcccd63dd520ef","tid":2140561,"uid":265449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T08:42:23.000Z","msg":"要係破產之前用盡白手套<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f493de8377de1f26ed4f8a7c1802be8cb3cfbdd","tid":2140561,"uid":43414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T08:54:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f3e6abfd129cc598c8e59bbdfb44c093c83d8c6e","tid":2140561,"uid":198040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc70be6ad10977efc1271ff9fb34c7342fea63fa","tid":2140561,"uid":263577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2114a58b9de5971721060d7f3a0866e2c717e2a8","tid":2140561,"uid":198040,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4dab05503